data.description: Owner is Agent!!Located just two minutes from Bass Pro and seven minutes from MSU! Newly renovated home with fresh paint in living quarters, kitchen cabinets, and bedrooms! All windows under five years old. New gutters/soffits/fascia in 2018. Beautifully redone wood burning fireplace in the living room to go with lvp and a nice updated accent entry wall! The kitchen features a brand new dishwasher and a three year old refrigerator, along with a nice stainless steel oven and microwave. The home features two full bathrooms, the master being a walk in shower with dual shower heads! Big spacious backyard perfect for kids or animals, comes included with new storage shed!
